des:
Welcome to X Minus One Radio where each week we will explore the from the far horizons of the unknown come transcribed tales of new dimensions in time and space. These are stories of the future; Countdown for blastoff... X minus five, four, three, two, X minus one... Fire! 

X Minus One is an American half-hour science fiction radio drama series that broadcast from April 24, 1955 to January 9, 1958 in various timeslots on Radio. Known for high production values in adapting stories from the leading American authors of the era, X Minus One has been described as one of the finest offerings of American radio drama and one of the best science fiction series in any medium.

(Public Domain)
